                    <span>It has been said many times that Wallace Stevens is one of the five best and most influential American poets. After reading this collection of poems it is impossible to disagree. It is a marvelous experience to pick up this book and read a few poems.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Iffucan, read this book and then have some ice-cream!</div>
